data.title: Ustad Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan
data.meta_description:
An actual name/address plate from the residence of Ustad Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan, located in Naimat colony right next to Rehmat Gramophone Studio, (where I use to train and where he had recorded his very earlier work before becoming a world known figure in international music), in Faisalabad, Pakistan.
	I Rescued it from kids playing cricket on the street who had scattered it.
	Its written in Urdu and  reads as follows: 
	Ustad Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan
	Street Number 8, P432 Naimat Colony Number 1.
